title: Week 14 Picks, Browns Fire Brown (Football 12/08)
description:
Will Brinson, Nick Kostos, Pete Prisco and Jason La Canfora are back on the Pick Six podcast for Week 14 picks against the spread. Before JLC's newly named "Scandinavian Death Metal Lock of the Week," he and Will react to the Browns firing personnel czar Sashi Brown. Then, Nick and Pete join Will to pick every game in Week 14, featuring games like Vikings-Panthers, Cowboys-Giants, Eagles-Rams and Ravens-Steelers.
